0Animal%20trailer%20reminds%20fans%20of%20Sanju%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700795112000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105458952%2Cimgsize-26362.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoors-animal-trailer-reminds-fans-of-sanju-performance-ranbir-looking-like-came-straight-out-from-sanju-set%2Farticleshow%2F105458799.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105458799.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20much-anticipated%20trailer%20for%20Ranbir%20Kapoor's%20upcoming%20film%20'Animal'%20on%20November%2023%20set%20social%20media%20abuzz.%20Fans%20noticed%20the%20uncanny%20resemblance%20between%20Kapoor's%20new%20role%20in%20'Animal'%20and%20his%20previous%20role%20as%20Sanjay%20Dutt%20in%20'Sanju'.%20The%20trailer%20left%20fans%20swooning%20over%20Kapoor's%20transformation%2C%20but%20some%20couldn't%20shake%20off%20his%20striking%20likeness%20to%20Dutt.%20Social%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20hashtags%20like%20%23SanjayDutt%20and%20%23Sanju%2C%20with%20fans%20amazed%20at%20the%20resemblance.%20The%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%2C%20is%20a%20gritty%20story%20about%20a%20father-son%20relationship%20and%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%20December%201.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franbir-kapoors-animal-trailer-reminds-fans-of-sanju-performance-ranbir-looking-like-came-straight-out-from-sanju-set%2Farticleshow%2F105458799.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20To%20Release%2013%20Hostages%20Today%20After%20Israel%20Pauses%20Gaza%20Attack%3A%20Qatar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ceasefire%20would%20begin%20at%2010.30%20am%20IST%2C%20while%20the%20first%20group%20of%20hostages%20will%20be%20released%20by%20Hamas%20hours%20later%2C%20around%207.30%20pm%20IST%2C%20according%20to%20Qatar's%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20batch%26quot%3B%20of%20civilian%20hostages%20would%20consist%20of%2013%20women%20and%20children%20from%20the%20same%20families.%C2%A0%20The%20number%20would%20rise%20up%20to%2050%20over%20the%20four%20days%2C%20according%20to%20the%20deal%20brokered%20by%20Qatar%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20office%20of%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20it%20was%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20families%20of%20the%20hostages%20after%20receiving%20%26quot%3Ba%20first%20list%20of%20names%26quot%3B%20of%20those%20due%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPalestinian%20prisoners%20held%20in%20Israeli%20jails%20would%20also%20be%20released%20on%20Friday%2C%20Qatari%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Majed%20Al%20Ansari%20said%2C%20adding%20a%20list%20of%20names%20had%20been%20approved%2C%20without%20saying%20how%20many.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20accord%20was%20orchestrated%20by%20Qatar%20and%20the%20US%20and%20officially%20announced%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20secretive%20effort%20included%20tense%20personal%20diplomatic%20engagement%20by%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20held%20a%20number%20of%20urgent%20conversations%20with%20the%20emir%20of%20Qatar%20and%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20agreement%20entailed%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20ceasefire%20with%20no%20attacks%20from%20the%20air%20or%20the%20ground%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20skies%20clear%20of%20drones%20to%20%26quot%3Ballow%20for%20the%20hostage%20release%20to%20happen%20in%20a%20safe%20environment%26quot%3B.%20Hamas%20confirmed%20the%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20would%20start%20at%2010.30%20am%20IST%20under%20the%20deal%20that%20is%20also%20intended%20to%20provide%20aid%20to%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20residents%20struggling%20to%20survive%20with%20shortages%20of%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20fuel.%20It%20said%20a%20total%20of%2050%20hostages%20--%20females%2C%20and%20males%20aged%2018%20or%20under%20--%20would%20be%20freed%2C%20with%20three%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20to%20be%20released%20for%20each%20of%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20Defence%20Forces%20have%20launched%20an%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20since%201%2C200%20citizens%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207.%20Hamas%20had%20also%20taken%20nearly%20240%20hostages%2C%20mostly%20civilians%20when%20their%20operatives%20burst%20across%20the%20border%20fence%20and%20raided%20towns%20in%20Southern%20Israel.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESince%20then%2C%20some%2013%2C000%20Gazans%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20Israeli%20bombardment%2C%20around%2040%25%20of%20them%20children%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20health%20authorities.%20However%2C%20they%20have%20said%20it%20has%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20keep%20an%20up-to-date%20tally%20as%20the%20health%20service%20has%20buckled%20under%20the%20Israeli%20bombardment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInternational%20pressure%20has%20been%20growing%20on%20Israel%20to%20end%20the%20war%20amid%20a%20risk%20of%20the%20conflict%20escalating%20and%20spilling%20into%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Iran-backed%20Hezbollah%20group%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20US%2C%20has%20launched%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20from%20Southern%20Lebanon.%20The%20group%20said%20it%20launched%2048%20Katyusha%20rockets%20at%20an%20Israeli%20army%20base%20earlier%20today.%20Israel%20said%20it%20intercepted%20some%20of%20them%20and%20struck%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700794920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdofccdsg_israel-attack-in-ga