%98Perhaps%20home%20is%20not%20a%20place%20but%20simply%20an%20irrevocable%20condition.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%93%20James%20Arthur%20Baldwin%2C%201924%E2%80%931987%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slope%20was%20red%20with%20bricks%20and%20blood.%20More%20bricks%20dropped%20from%20the%20sky%20like%20missiles.%20Once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20a%20bottle%20of%20acid%20or%20a%20petrol%20bomb%20made%20its%20presence%20felt%20among%20the%20variety%20of%20objects%20being%20hurled.%20Amid%20the%20clash%20of%20religious%20slogans%20and%20verbal%20abuses%2C%20gunshots%20were%20heard.%20The%20riot%20was%20at%20its%20zenith%20%E2%80%93%20and%20my%20home%20lay%20exactly%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnger%20rose%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20men%20flooding%20the%20streets.%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHar%20har%20Mahadev!%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20they%20shouted%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20slope.%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAllahu%20Akbar!%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20shouted%20other%20angry%20men%20from%20the%20top%20of%20the%20slope.%20The%20body%20of%20a%20twenty-year-old%20boy%20lay%20somewhere%20between%20this%20mass%20of%20angry%20men%2C%20his%20intestines%20ripped%20out%2C%20his%20blood%20spreading%20across%20the%20tarmac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20406px)%2085vw%2C%20406px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23142829%2Fimage-1530.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22406%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23142829%2Fimage-1530.png%20468w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23142829%2Fimage-1530-191x300.png%20191w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22638%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECity%20on%20Fire%2C%20Zeyad%20Masroor%20Khan%2C%20HarperCollins%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20memory%20that%20haunts%20me%20the%20most%20is%20the%20sound%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20screams%20coming%20from%20all%20directions%20at%20once.%20As%20if%20all%20the%20women%20in%20my%20mohalla%20were%20screaming%20in%20unison.%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EYa%20Allah!%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20cried%20an%20old%20woman%20standing%20in%20a%20balcony%20in%20front%20of%20the%20foyer%20of%20my%20house%2C%20wiping%20tears%20with%20her%20dupatta.%20Her%20daughter%20called%20out%20to%20her%20brother%20urgently%2C%20repeatedly.%20%E2%80%98Faisal!%20Faisal!%20Come%20back!%E2%80%99%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20had%20noticed%20these%20particular%20neighbours.%20The%20woman%20started%20breaking%20away%20loose%20bricks%20from%20her%20balcony%20wall%20and%20dropping%20them%20out%20to%20Faisal.%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20give%20them%20an%20inch%20or%20they%E2%80%99ll%20enter%20our%20homes!%E2%80%99%20she%20cried.%20Almost%20everyone%20picks%20a%20side%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20staying%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20shortage%20of%20bricks%20on%20our%20side%20of%20the%20fight.%20An%20unlucky%20neighbour%20had%20ordered%20a%20truckful%20a%20few%20days%20ago.%20Nobody%20asked%20his%20permission%20before%20taking%20a%20whole%20slab%20away%20to%20be%20used%20as%20weapons.%20Some%20men%20went%20inside%20an%20old%20house%20and%20demolished%20a%20broken%20wall%20for%20more%20arsenal%20to%20attack%20the%20marauding%20enemy.%20Apart%20from%20this%20advantage%2C%20we%20were%20also%20at%20a%20height.%20So%2C%20when%20the%20Hindu%20mob%20tried%20to%20push%20up%20the%20slope%2C%20they%20were%20easily%20turned%20back.%20%E2%80%98I%20will%20return%20and%20fuck%20your%20mother%20in%20front%20of%20you%2C%E2%80%99%20cried%20one%20of%20them%20as%20a%20part%20of%20a%20brick%20hit%20his%20head%20and%20blood%20gushed%20down%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20they%20returned%20with%20more%20guns%2C%20and%20all%20our%20advantages%20turned%20to%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20our%20home%2C%20my%20mother%20was%20trying%20to%20decide%20whether%20it%20was%20time%20to%20run.%20She%20was%20reading%20%3Cem%3EAyatul%20Kursi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20verse%20Muslims%20read%20when%20they%20are%20afraid.%20My%20father%20was%20at%20his%20office%20at%20the%20university%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20town.%20Mother%20told%20my%20elder%20brother%2C%20Saad%2C%20to%20keep%20a%20watch%20and%20gauge%20the%20danger%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20came%20back%20in%20a%20rush.%20%E2%80%98Ammi%2C%20bullets%20are%20being%20fired%20from%20everywhere.%20One%20missed%20my%20ear%20by%20a%20few%20inches%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20said%2C%20sounding%20more%20excited%20than%20afraid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Did%20it%20really%20go%20past%20your%20ear%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20lie%2C%E2%80%99%20I%20asked%20circumspectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20could%20answer%2C%20Sayema%2C%20our%20sister%2C%20began%20to%20cry.%20She%20had%20been%20calling%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20office%20landline%20from%20her%20Nokia%201100%20phone%20non-stop.%20Her%20husband%20had%20given%20her%20this%20brand-new%20phone%20with%20an%20orange%20keypad%20before%20she%20left%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20come%20home%20to%20deliver%20their%20first%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20eight-month-old%20baby%20in%20Sayema%E2%80%99s%20belly%20was%20our%20primary%20concern.%20Running%20away%20involved%20the%20risk%20that%20she%20%E2%80%93%20or%20anyone%20else%20among%20us%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20shot.%20Or%20Hindus%20could%20enter%20our%20house%20through%20the%20garage%20door%20and%20set%20it%20on%20fire%20(like%20they%20once%20had%20when%20Sayema%20was%20one).%20As%20my%20mother%20weighed%20her%20options%2C%20four%20strange%20men%20rushed%20into%20our%20home.%20%E2%80%98Baaji%2C%20we%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20terrace%20to%20attack%20enemies%20from%20a%20height.%20Unlock%20your%20staircase%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20the%20shortest%20among%20them%2C%20his%20eyes%20wet%20with%20tears%20of%20anger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Forgive%20us%2C%20for%20Allah%E2%80%99s%20sake!%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20our%20home%20used%20for%20rioting%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20my%20mother%20as%20she%20pushed%20them%20out%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98We%20are%20fighting%20to%20save%20you.%20If%20not%20for%20us%2C%20they%E2%80%99d%20have%20entered%20your%20homes%20by%20now%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20said%20before%20going%20away%20to%20knock%20on%20other%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20latched%20our%20door%2C%20I%20heard%20the%20sound%20of%20stones%20hitting%20the%20ground.%20It%20was%20coming%20from%20across%20the%20foyer%20in%20Palle%20Ghar%2C%20the%20portion%20of%20our%20ancestral%20home%20inhabited%20by%20the%20twenty-one%20members%20of%20my%20paternal%20aunt%E2%80%99s%20family.%20The%20attack%20had%20arrived%20there.%20I%20saw%20bricks%20raining%20down%20her%20porch%2C%20bypassing%20the%20giant%20peepal%20tree%20separating%20her%20home%20from%20Hindu%20neighbours.%20%E2%80%98I%20have%20spent%20my%20whole%20life%20here%20but%20%3Cem%3Enever%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseen%20such%20bad%20times%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20Mehro%2C%20my%20Phuppo%2C%20blankness%20reigning%20in%20her%20green%20eyes.%20Her%20sons%20had%20moved%20their%20children%20to%20safe%20places%2C%20far%20away%20from%20bricks%20and%20bullets.%20Two%20of%20the%20sons%20and%20their%20families%20would%20leave%20this%20home%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20Palle%20Ghar%20had%20also%20opened%20up%20another%20grim%20possibility%3A%20people%20firing%20bullets%20at%20our%20house.%20%E2%80%98The%20Hindus%20are%20standing%20with%20guns%20on%20their%20terrace.%20I%20saw%20somebody%20firing%20from%20the%20roof%20of%20Punjab%20Bank%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20Nadim%20Bhai%2C%20Phuppo%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20son.%20Anyone%20standing%20on%20their%20terrace%20now%20scared%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Ammi%2C%20should%20I%20close%20the%20window%3F%20They%20can%20see%20us%20moving%20inside%20our%20house%2C%E2%80%99%20I%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20act%20too%20smart.%20Stay%20away%20from%20the%20windows%2C%E2%80%99%20she%20said%2C%20reciting%20another%20set%20of%20%3Cem%3Edua%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20the%20women%20of%20Palle%20Ghar.%20I%20shut%20the%20window.%20I%20wanted%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20seeing%20us%20moving%20around%20our%20living%20room.%20My%20brother%20promptly%20switched%20off%20the%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuddenly%2C%20Tariq%20Bhai%2C%20my%20paternal%20cousin%2C%20came%20rushing%20into%20our%20living%20room.%20%E2%80%98They%20are%20trying%20to%20climb%20up.%20You%20should%20run%20across%20the%20lane%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98What%20about%20Sayema%3F%E2%80%99%20Ammi%20asked%2C%20pointing%20to%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20eight-month-old%20stomach%20bulge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Let%E2%80%99s%20walk%20slowly%2C%E2%80%99%20said%20Saad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20the%20panic%2C%20Ammi%20took%20her%20time%20to%20lock%20the%20doors%20and%20hide%20anything%20that%20had%20a%20remote%20chance%20of%20being%20stolen.%20Finally%2C%20we%20left%20our%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%2C%20the%20screams%20of%20women%20mingled%20with%20gunshots%2C%20profanity%20and%20religious%20slogans%20to%20create%20a%20strange%20cacophony%20of%20chaos.%20We%20walked%20holding%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20hands%20before%20running%20into%20a%20narrow%20lane%20that%20led%20towards%20Jama%20Masjid.%20%E2%80%98This%20way!%20This%20way!%E2%80%99%20said%20neighbourhood%20women%20we%20had%20never%20met%2C%20showing%20us%20the%20way%20to%20run%20away%20from%20our%20home%20while%20they%20were%20firmly%20planted%20in%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20left%2C%20the%20four%20strangers%20who%20wanted%20to%20enter%20our%20terrace%20returned%20to%20our%20home.%20They%20broke%20the%20rusty%20lock%20on%20the%20staircase.%20One%20of%20them%20later%20died%20of%20a%20bullet%20wound%20in%20a%20clinic%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20later%20that%20I%20found%20out%20that%20Shadab%20had%20also%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EZeyad%20Masroor%20Khan%20is%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%20and%20documentary%20film-maker%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20In%20his%20decade-long%20journalistic%20career%2C%20he%20has%20worked%20with%20national%20and%20international%20media%20companies%20like%20%3C%2Fem%3EReuters%2C%20Vice%2C%20Brut%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20Deccan%20Herald.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700794895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24082915%2F339836345_6ec5c293e6_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcity-of-fire-book-growing-up-as-muslim-aligarh-babri-riots%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'City%20on%20Fire'%20is%20a%20rare%20visceral%20portrait%20of%20how%20everyday%20violence%20and%20hate%20become%20a%20part%20of%20our%20lives%20and%20consciousness%3B%20a%20society%20where%20name%20and%20clothes%20mark%20out%20a%20person%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcity-of-fire-book-growing-up-as-muslim-aligarh-babri-riots%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDecision%20Result%20Of%20Broader%20Changes%26quot%3B%3A%20Afghan%20Embassy%20Shuts%20In%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghanistan%20embassy%20has%20announced%20its%20permanent%20closure%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReleasing%20an%20official%20statement%20on%20the%20closure%20of%20its%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEffective%20from%20November%2023%2C%202023%20owing%20to%20persistent%20challenges%20from%20the%20Indian%20government.%20The%20decision%20follows%20the%20embassy's%20earlier%20cessation%20of%20operations%20on%20September%2030%2C%20a%20move%20made%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20stance%20will%20favourably%20change%20to%20let%20the%20mission%20operate%20normally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20said%20it%20was%20'cognisant'%20that%20some%20may%20attempt%20to%20characterise%20this%20move%20as%20an%20internal%20conflict%2C%20allegedly%20involving%20diplomats%20who%20switched%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Taliban%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bthat%20this%20decision%20is%20a%20result%20of%20broader%20changes%20in%20policy%20and%20interests%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20Afghan%20citizens%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Embassy%20extends%20its%20sincere%20gratitude%20for%20their%20understanding%20and%20support%20throughout%20our%20mission's%20tenure%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20%26quot%3Blimitations%20in%20resources%20and%20power%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20said%20it%20has%20worked%20%26quot%3Btirelessly%20for%20their%20betterment%20and%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20legitimate%20government%20in%20Kabul%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%20and%20three%20months%2C%20the%20Afghan%20community%20in%20India%20has%20witnessed%20a%20significant%20decline%2C%20with%20Afghan%20refugees%2C%20students%2C%20and%20traders%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%20the%20embassy%20noted%20in%20its%20statement%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20number%20has%20nearly%20halved%20since%20August%202021%2C%20with%20very%20limited%20new%20visas%20being%20issued%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20assure%20the%20Afghan%20community%20that%20the%20mission%20operated%20with%20transparency%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20a%20commitment%20to%20fair%20treatment%20based%20on%20the%20goodwill%20and%20interests%20of%20Afghanistan%20considering%20historic%20ties%20and%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20efforts%20have%20been%20made%20to%20tarnish%20our%20image%20and%20hinder%20diplomatic%20efforts%20in%20order%20to%20justify%20the%20presence%20and%20work%20of%20Taliban-appointed%20and%20affiliated%20diplomats.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20these%20challenges%2C%20our%20committed%20team%20worked%20diligently%20in%20the%20most%20difficult%20circumstances%2C%20prioritizing%20the%20interests%20of%20the%2040%20million%20Afghans%20in%20every%20possible%20sphere%20from%20securing%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20online%20education%20scholarships%20to%20facilitating%20ease%20in%20trade%20and%20advocating%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20broad-based%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20stated%20further%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20%26quot%3Bexerted%20diplomatic%20pressure%20in%20its%20power%20on%20those%20who%20defy%20the%20will%20of%20the%20Afghan%20people%20by%20failing%20to%20form%20an%20inclusive%20government%20and%20denying%20millions%20of%20girls%20the%20right%20to%20attend%20school%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20there%20are%20no%20diplomats%20from%20the%20Afghan%20Republic%20in%20India.%20Those%20who%20served%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20have%20safely%20reached%20third%20countries%2C%20the%20embassy%20informed%20through%20its%20release%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20only%20individuals%20present%20in%20India%20are%20diplomats%20affiliated%20with%20the%20Taliban%2C%20visibly%20attending%20their%20regular%20online%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20diplomats%20of%20the%20Afghan%20Republic%20have%20handed%20over%20the%20mission%20solely%20to%20the%20Indian%20government.%20It%20now%20rests%20upon%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20mission%2C%20whether%20to%20maintain%20its%20closure%20or%20consider%20alternatives%2C%20including%20the%20possibility%20of%20handing%20it%20over%20to%20Taliban%20diplomats.%20The%20responsibility%20of%20diplomats%20appointed%20by%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Afghanistan%20has%20officially%20come%20to%20an%20end.%20The%20unfortunate%20end%20of%20the%20Republic%20mission%20marks%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Afghan%20Republic%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20considered%20the%20historic%20events%20and%20current%20circumstances%20carefully%20in%20arriving%20at%20this%20conclusion.%20We%20also%20extend%20our%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India%20for%20their%20support%20and%20assistance%20to%20Afghanistan%20over%20the%20past%2022%20years.%20We%20reiterate%20our%20commitment%20to%20serving%20the%20people%20of%20Afghanistan%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20explore%20avenues%20to%20support%20our%20nation%20in%20these%20challenging%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Afghan%20embassy%20announced%20the%20closure%20of%20its%20operations%20on%20November%201%2C%20citing%20%26quot%3Black%20of%20resources%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfailure%20to%20meet%20Afghanistan's%20interests%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Taliban%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20also%20made%20an%20%26quot%3Bunequivocal%20statement%26quot%3B%20stating%20that%20certain%20consulates%20that%20work%20on%20the%20instructions%20and%20funding%20from%20Kabul%20are%20not%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20objectives%20of%20a%20legitimate%20or%20elected%20government%20but%20rather%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Billegitimate%20regime%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700794860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F157ja64_afghanistan-embassy-delhi_625x300_01_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafghanistan-embassy-announces-permanent-closure-in-delhi-4601468%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22T