20overwhelming%2C%20don't%20let%20yourself%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20craze.%20Below%20are%20some%20of%20the%20best%20tips%20for%20balancing%20deal-hunting%20with%20preventing%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20ways%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20Black%20Friday%20deals%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKnow%20what%20you're%20looking%20for%20and%20make%20a%20list.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20go%20shopping%2C%20whether%20online%20or%20in-store%2C%20make%20a%20list%20of%20things%20you%20want%20or%20need%20to%20avoid%20impulse%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigure%20out%20who%20you%20want%20a%20gift%20for%2C%20or%20what%20you%20hope%20to%20find%20on%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20set%20list%20can%20help%20you%20avoid%20impulse%20buying%20or%20being%20drawn%20to%20steep%20discounts%20just%20because%20they%20seem%20like%20a%20good%20deal.%20You%20probably%20don't%20need%20it%20if%20you%20didn't%20think%20about%20the%20item%20before%20seeing%20it%20on%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUse%20online%20tools%20to%20help%20you%20find%20the%20best%20prices.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20wealth%20of%20apps%20and%20extensions%20that%20can%20help%20you%20look%20for%20coupons%20and%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20be%20afraid%20to%20take%20a%20second%20and%20use%20these%20tools%20to%20compare%20prices%20on%20different%20websites%2C%20or%20to%20clip%20coupons%20for%20use%20in-store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPlan%20which%20credit%20card%20to%20use%20for%20which%20purchases.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20credit%20card%20interest%20rates%20and%20rewards%20vary%2C%20planning%20what%20card%20to%20use%20when%20you%20buy%20an%20item%20can%20help%20you%20avoid%20extra%20costs%20and%20help%20you%20save%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20your%20card%20gives%20you%203%25%20cash%20back%20on%20electronics%20stores%2C%20use%20it%20when%20you%20want%20your%20new%20TV%20or%20devices.%20You%20may%20also%20want%20to%20avoid%20using%20a%20specific%20card%20that%20has%20a%20high%20interest%20rate%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20know%20it%20will%20take%20you%20time%20to%20pay%20off%20your%20holiday%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20your%20cards%20to%20find%20what%20looks%20best%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20credit%20card%20can%20also%20pick%20smarter%20by%20choosing%20a%20card%20with%20a%200%25%20intro%20APR%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fthe-ascent%2Fpersonal-finance%2Farticles%2F5-ways-to-stretch-out-your-holiday-shopping-budget%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMotley%20Fool%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20rate%20means%20customers%20could%20have%20a%20longer%20time%20to%20pay%20off%20their%20purchases%20from%20the%20holiday%20without%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOr%2C%20if%20you%20have%20trouble%20using%20cards%2C%20pay%20in%20cash%20%E2%80%94%20and%20use%20big%20bills.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20not%20alone%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20get%20carried%20away%20when%20you're%20swiping%20your%20card.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmitsloan.mit.edu%2Fexperts%2Fhow-credit-cards-activate-reward-center-our-brains-and-drive-spending%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20credit%20cards%20can%20trigger%20the%20%26quot%3Brewards%26quot%3B%20part%20of%20your%20brain%2C%20making%20you%20more%20likely%20to%20spend%20excessively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20use%20cash%2C%20you%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20conscious%20of%20just%20how%20much%20you're%20spending.%20Using%20cash%20can%20help%20you%20spend%20between%2010%25%20and%2015%25%20less%20than%20you%20would%20with%20a%20credit%20card%2C%20according%20to%20financial%20expert%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyfit.org%2Fimpulse-spending%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETodd%20Christensen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConsider%20%26quot%3Bextras%26quot%3B%20when%20you%20budget.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20other%20things%20that%20might%20be%20incorporated%20into%20your%20gift-giving%20costs.%20Do%20you%20want%20to%20use%20wrapping%20paper%20or%20gift%20bags%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20to%20mail%20your%20gifts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20small%20costs%20can%20catch%20up%20to%20you%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20know%20what%20you%20want%20to%20spend%20on%20things%20like%20presentation%20and%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDon't%20get%20caught%20up%20with%20quantity%20over%20quality%20of%20gifts.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBudgeting%20for%20a%20gift%20for%20someone%20is%20a%20great%20idea%2C%20but%20it%20might%20be%20easy%20to%20think%20you%20have%20to%20spend%20that%20much%20on%20them%20no%20matter%20what%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20unnecessary%20and%20less%20thoughtful%20giving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20you%20need%20to%20spend%20%24100%20on%20your%20children%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20might%20feel%20obligated%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20up%26quot%3B%20and%20buy%20more%20if%20a%20gift%20ends%20up%20coming%20in%20under%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20worrying%20about%20matching%20costs%20between%20people%20or%20your%20planned%20budget%2C%20find%20a%20meaningful%20gift%2C%20and%20don't%20think%20hitting%20a%20set%20price%20point%20means%20caring%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGift%20cards%20can%20also%20be%20a%20great%20and%20versatile%20gift%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20outlets%20sell%20card%20packages%20for%20less%20than%20the%20amount%20on%20each%20card.%20It's%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20give%20more%20while%20spending%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECommon%20schemes%20to%20avoid%20on%20Black%20Friday%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3EWatch%20for%20%26quot%3Bdoorbuster%20deals%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20don't%20buy%20just%20because%20of%20large%20discounts.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELots%20of%20deals%20are%20actually%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20NerdWallet%20finance%20expert%20Kimberly%20Palmer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fblack-friday-shopping-tips-deals-tricks-holidays-nerd-wallet-discounts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank