6quot%3BFor%20the%20court%20to%20direct%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20reservation%20made%20...%20Parliament%20must%20legislate%20to%20enact%20proportional%20representation%20for%20all%20other%20communities%20forming%20part%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20that%20would%20be%20venturing%20into%20the%20legislative%20domain%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20directions%20were%20issued%20by%20a%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20on%20a%20plea%20seeking%20a%20proportionate%20representation%20of%20the%20Limbu%20and%20Tamang%20tribal%20communities%20in%20the%20assemblies%20of%20Sikkim%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20they%20(Centre)%20have%20to%20set%20up%20the%20delimitation%20commission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%20It%20said%20the%20top%20court%20has%20the%20power%20of%20judicial%20review%20to%20determine%20whether%20a%20provision%20enacted%20by%20Parliament%20is%20unconstitutional%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthis%20court%20will%20go%20beyond%20the%20line%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDealing%20with%20proportionate%20representation%20of%20communities%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20it%20would%20require%20using%20the%20power%20under%20the%20Delimitation%20Act%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20provides%20for%20a%20readjustment%20of%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20in%20state%20assemblies%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20Assembly%20seats%20and%20the%20division%20of%20each%20state%20and%20Union%20Territory%20having%20a%20legislative%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20regard%20to%20the%20state%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20it%20has%20been%20submitted%20that%20...%20additional%20seats%20have%20to%20be%20made%20available%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly%20for%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20order%20to%20accommodate%20the%20principle%20of%20proportional%20representation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20above%20circumstance%20makes%20it%20abundantly%20necessary%20for%20the%20Centre%20to%20take%20recourse%20to%20power%20under%20the%20Delimitation%20Act%2C%202002%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20provisions%20under%20articles%20332%20and%20333%20of%20the%20Constitution%20are%20duly%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20its%20verdict%20%26quot%3Bshall%20not%20be%20read%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20elections%20to%20Parliament%20or%20state%20assemblies%20since%20elections%20are%20an%20overarching%20mandate%20and%20they%20have%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20on%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20Centre%20must%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsidered%20view%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20reconstitution%20of%20the%20delimitation%20commission%20to%20ensure%20a%20proportional%20representation%20of%20the%20Limbu%20and%20Tamang%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20said%20the%20demand%20of%20the%20communities%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20proportional%20representation%20has%20a%20constitutional%20foundation%2C%20which%20can%20be%20found%20in%20articles%20330%20and%20332.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20we%20are%20conscious%20that%20we%20cannot%20direct%20Parliament%20to%20enact%20a%20law%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20must%20take%20a%20considered%20view%20if%20the%20delimitation%20commission%20should%20be%20reconstituted%20to%20ensure%20justice%20to%20those%20communities%20who%20have%20been%20designated%20as%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20Centre%20to%20discuss%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20respond%20to%20it%20by%20Thursday.%20The%20Centre%20on%20Thursday%20said%20the%20issue%20has%20to%20be%20left%20to%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20start%2C%20the%20benefit%20(of%20reservation)%20has%20to%20be%20given%20across%20the%20country%20and%20there%20are%20already%20demands%20from%20various%20states.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20done%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre's%20counsel%20said%2C%20adding%20that%2052%20communities%2C%20which%20were%20in%20the%20general%20pool%20earlier%2C%20have%20been%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20SCs%20and%20STs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20moved%20by%20the%20Public%20Interest%20Committee%20for%20Scheduling%20Specific%20Areas%20(PICSSA)%2C%20an%20NGO%2C%20which%20argued%20that%20the%20Limbu%20and%20Tamang%20communities%2C%20both%20belonging%20to%20the%20ST%20category%2C%20have%20been%20denied%20a%20proportionate%20representation%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20appearing%20in%20the%20court%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20NGO%2C%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20ST%20population%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20West%20Bengal%20and%20not%20reserving%20seats%20for%20them%20proportionate%20to%20the%20growth%20amounted%20to%20a%20denial%20of%20their%20constitutional%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20plea%2C%20the%20NGO%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Limbu%20and%20Tamang%20communities%20in%20Sikkim%20was%2020.6%20per%20cent%20in%202001%20and%20had%20risen%20to%2033.8%20per%20cent%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20said%20that%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20area%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20ST%20population%20rose%20to%2021.5%20per%20cent%20in%202011%20from%2012.69%20per%20cent%20in%202001.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PIL%20has%20sought%20directions%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20and%20the%20two%20states%20to%20take%20steps%20for%20a%20proportional%20representation%20of%20the%20STs%2C%20as%20guaranteed%20under%20articles%20330%20(reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20SCs%20and%20STs%20in%20the%20House%20of%20People)%20and%20332%20(reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20SCs%20and%20STs%20in%20legislative%20assemblies%20of%20states)%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20to%20prevent%20a%20violation%20of%20Article%2014%20(equality%20before%20law).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20in%20the%20Tribes%20Advisory%20Council%20established%20in%20West%20Bengal%20on%20March%206%2C%202012%2C%20there%20were%20no%20elected%20ST%20members%20from%20the%20three%20hill%20area%20sub-divisions%20of%20Darjeeling%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20the%20state%20Assembly%20election%20in%202016%20had%20no%20reserved%20ST%20seat%20and%20hence%2C%20had%20no%20implementation%20of%20articles%20170%20and%20332%20of%20the%20Constitution%20notified%20as%20per%20census%202011.%20The%20delimited%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20hills%20presently%20consist%20of%20elected%20non-ST%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700791860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fc5p4n3lg_supreme-court-premises_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-asks-centre-to-set-up-new-panel-for-sc-st-representation-4600550%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20the%20Centre%20on%20Thursday%20to%20set%20up%20a%20fresh%20delimitation%20commission%20for%20ensuring%20a%20proportional%20representation%20of%20the%20communities%20specified%20as%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-asks-centre-to-set-up-new-panel-for-sc-st-representation-4600550%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-asks-centre-to-set-up-new-panel-for-sc-st-representation-4600550%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-asks-centre-to-set-up-new-panel-for-sc-st-representation-4600550%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There%20is%20only%20one%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%3A%20Kareena%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700791794000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105458397%2Cimgsize-39396.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthere-is-only-one-ranbir-kapoor-says-kareena-kapoor-khan-after-watching-animals-trailer%2Farticleshow%2F105458417.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105458417.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKareena%20Kapoor%20praises%20Ranbir's%20transformative%20role%20in%20%26quot%3BAnimal%2C%26quot%3B%20emphasizing%20there's%20only%20one%20Ranbir.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthere-is-only-one-ranbir-kapoor-says-kareena-kapoor-khan-after-watching-animals-trailer%2Farticleshow%2F105458417.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Violent%20Clashes%20In%20Dublin%20After%20Children%20Stabbed%20Outside%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EProtesters%20on%20Thursday%20fought%20running%20battles%20with%20police%2C%20torched%20vehicles%20and%20looted%20shops%20in%20Dublin%2C%20after%20three%20young%20children%20were%20injured%20in%20a%20knife%20attack%20outside%20a%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20in%20riot%20gear%20stood%20guard%20on%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20Irish%20capital%20as%20crowds%20taunted%20them%20with%20chants%20and%20set%20off%20fireworks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENear%20O'Connell%20Bridge%2C%20over%20the%20River%20Liffey%2C%20flames%20rose%20from%20a%20torched%20car%20and%20bus%2C%20while%20crowds%20broke%20into%20stores%20and%20looted%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20main%20shopping%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unrest%20--%20the%20worst%20in%20Dublin%20in%20years%20--%20came%20after%20a%20five-year-old%20girl%20sustained%20serious%20injuries%20in%20a%20suspected%20stabbing%20in%20Parnell%20Square%20East%2C%20north%20central%20Dublin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20children%20and%20two%20adults%20--%20a%20woman%20and%20the%20suspected%20perpetrator%20of%20the%20attack%20--%20were%20taken%20to%20hospital%20after%20the%20incident%20around%201%3A30%20pm%20(1330%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERumours%20on%20social%20media%20about%20the%20nationality%20of%20the%20assailant%2C%20who%20police%20only%20described%20as%20a%20man%20in%20his%20fifties%2C%20helped%20fuel%20unrest%20following%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20chief%20Drew%20Harris%20blamed%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20lunatic%20faction%20driven%20by%20far-right%20ideology%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20against%20%26quot%3Bmisinformation%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20protesters%20carried%20signs%20reading%20%26quot%3BIrish%20Lives%20Matter%26quot%3B%20and%20waved%20Irish%20flags%20through%20a%20neighbourhood%20home%20to%20a%20large%20immigrant%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20protester%20told%20AFP%20that%20%26quot%3BIrish%20people%20are%20being%20attacked%20by%20these%20scum.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIreland%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20chronic%20housing%20crisis%2C%20with%20the%20government%20estimating%20that%20there%20is%20a%20deficit%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20homes%20for%20the%20general%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWidespread%20dissatisfaction%20has%20fed%20into%20a%20backlash%20against%20asylum%20seekers%20and%20refugees%2C%20and%20far-right%20figures%20have%20promoted%20anti-immigration%20sentiment%20at%20rallies%20and%20on%20social%20media%20with%20claims%20that%20%26quot%3BIreland%20is%20full%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20evening%2C%20Police%20Chief%20Superintendent%20Patrick%20McMenamin%20said%20calm%20had%20been%20restored%20and%20no%20serious%20injuries%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20gratuitous%20thuggery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBacklash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Minister%20Helen%20McEntee%20said%20the%20scenes%20in%20the%20city%20centre%2C%20including%20attacks%20on%20police%2C%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20and%20will%20not%20be%20tolerated%26quot%3B%20and%20promised%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20thuggish%20and%20manipulative%20element%20must%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20use%20an%20appalling%20tragedy%20to%20wreak%20havoc%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20calling%20for%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20incident%2C%20which%20police%20said%20was%20not%20thought%20to%20be%20terror-related%2C%20involved%20a%20man%20armed%20with%20a%20knife%20stabbing%20victims%20outside%20the%20school%2C%20according%20to%20media%20and%20eyewitnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20described%20how%20a%20man%20had%20been%20disarmed%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Leo%20Varadkar%20said%20a%20suspect%20had%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20Liam%20Geraghty%20later%20told%20media%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20young%20girl%20aged%20five%20years%20has%20sustained%20serious%20injuries%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20receiving%20emergency%20medical%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-year-old%20boy%20and%20a%20six-year-old%20girl%20sustained%20less%20serious%20wounds%20and%20the%20boy%20had%20since%20been%20discharged%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20serious%20injuries%20in%20hospital%2C%20while%20the%20man%2C%20said%20to%20be%20in%20his%2050s%2C%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bperson%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20for%20police%2C%20revealed%20Geraghty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiobhan%20Kearney%20said%20the%20scene%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20bedlam%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20initially%20watched%20events%20unfold%20from%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20thinking%2C%20I%20just%20took%20across%20the%20road%20to%20help%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Irish%20national%20broadcaster%20RTE.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20another%20young%20man%2C%20disarmed%20(the%20attacker)%20with%20the%20knife.%20Another%20man%20took%20the%20knife%20and%20put%20it%20away%20for%20the%20(police)%20to%20find%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKearney%20added%20a%20group%20of%20people%20restrained%20the%20suspect%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20some%20of%20those%20injured%20were%20taken%20back%20inside%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Horrified'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaradkar%20said%20he%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emergency%20services%20responded%20very%20quickly%20and%20were%20on%20site%20within%20minutes.%20I%20thank%20them%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGardai%20(Ireland's%20national%20police)%20have%20detained%20a%20suspect%20and%20are%20following%20a%20definite%20line%20of%20inquiry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20chief%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bbrutal%20attack%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20lawmaker%20Aodhan%20O%20Riordain%20of%20the%20Irish%20Labour%20Party%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisturbing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHope%20injuries%20are%20not%20serious%20but%20it%20will%20(be)%20extremely%20traumatising%20regardless%20for%20all%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%