.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%2041%20workers%20trapped%20under%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20will%20be%20pulled%20out%20on%20wheeled%20stretchers%20one%20by%20one%20through%20a%20big%20pipe%20that%20is%20still%20being%20drilled%20to%20reach%20them%2C%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20Director%20General%20Atul%20Karwal%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENDRF%20personnel%20will%20slide%20in%20through%20the%20pipe%20and%20once%20they%20reach%20the%20workers%2C%20they%20will%20use%20the%20stretchers%20to%20send%20out%20workers%20one%20by%20one%2C%20said%20Mr%20Karwal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEvery%20worker%20will%20be%20carefully%20positioned%20on%20a%20stretcher%20to%20prevent%20their%20limbs%20from%20scraping%20against%20the%20welded%20pipe's%20metal%20underside%20while%20NDRF%20personnel%20skillfully%20maneuver%20the%20stretcher%20with%20a%20rope.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20report%20of%20a%20possible%20earthquake%20which%20had%20happened%2C%20very%20low-intensity%2C%20very%20low%20on%20the%20Richter%20scale.%20It%20was%20missed%20by%20everyone%20at%20that%20particular%20time.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20part%20of%20climate%20or%20weather%20pattern%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hasnain%20said%20yesterday.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHIDCL)%20has%20re-initiated%20horizontal%20drilling%20from%20the%20Silkyara%20end%20to%20rescue%20trapped%20workers%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20an%20Auger%20boring%20machine%2C%20as%20per%20the%20government's%20latest%20media%20update.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rescue%20operation%20faced%20a%20setback%20when%20a%20metallic%20object%2C%20identified%20as%20a%20lattice%20girder%20rib%2C%20impeded%20the%20further%20insertion%20of%20the%20rescue%20pipe.%20At%202%3A30%20am%2C%20gas%20cutters%20were%20deployed%20to%20remove%20the%20metallic%20obstacle%2C%20allowing%20the%20pipe%20to%20be%20extended.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C