0concerned%20on%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Hand%2C%2063%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fuk-news%2F2023%2Fnov%2F20%2Femily-hands-father-pleads-for-hamas-to-release-her-amid-hope-of-hostage-deal%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20me%20hope%2C%20but%20until%20I%20see%20her%2C%20until%20I'm%20holding%20her%20I%20won't%20believe%20anything.%20Until%20I%20see%20it%2C%20I%20won't%20believe%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hand%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20London%20described%20his%20life%20as%20a%20nightmare.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20the%20Israeli%20government%20and%20the%20army%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20their%20capabilities%20to%20get%20them%20back.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmily%20was%20initially%20believed%20to%20be%20among%20the%201%2C200%20Israelis%20killed%20during%20the%20surprise%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20in%20southern%20Israel.%20Now%2C%20she%20is%20counted%20among%20the%20240%20hostages%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20sole%20purpose%20in%20life%20now%20is%20to%20do%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20get%20my%20little%20daughter%20Emily%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hand%2C%20who%20after%20living%20in%20Be'eri%20kibbutz%20for%2020%20years%20working%20in%20a%20printing%20house%2C%20now%20lives%20in%20a%20hotel%20near%20the%20Dead%20Sea.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20else%20concerns%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20on%20its%20Facebook%20page%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20beautiful%208-year-old%20girl%20Emily%20Hand%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20murdered%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20on%20October%207th.%20We%20now%20know%20she%20is%20being%20held%20hostage%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20in%20Gaza.%20Please%20share%20this%20and%20help%20us%20bring%20Emily%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FIsraelMFA%252Fvideos%252F314271228058272%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D264%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20deal%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20a%20four-day%20truce%20so%20that%2050%20women%20and%20children%20under%20the%20age%20of%2019%20taken%20hostage%20could%20be%20freed%20in%20return%20for%20150%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20teenagers%20in%20Israeli%20detention%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-day%20truce%20will%20start%20at%207%20am%20local%20time%20(05%3A00%20GMT)%20on%20Friday%20and%20the%20first%2013%20civilian%20captives%20will%20be%20released%20at%20about%204%20pm%20(14%3A00%20GMT)%2C%20the%20Qatari%20foreign%20ministry%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2050%20hostages%2C%20among%20about%20240%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20in%20their%20Oct.%207%20raid%20on%20Israel%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20released%20in%20batches%2C%20probably%20about%20a%20dozen%20a%20day%2C%20during%20the%20four-day%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20involved%20in%20the%20deal%20have%20described%20the%20break%20in%20hostilities%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20humanitarian%20pause%26quot%3B.%20The%20pause%20will%20be%20extended%20by%20a%20day%20for%20each%20additional%20batch%20of%2010%20hostages%20released%2C%20Israel%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hostages%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20transported%20through%20Egypt%2C%20the%20only%20country%20apart%20from%20Israel%20to%20share%20a%20border%20with%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700762040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F3ocmt5sg_emily-hand_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhamas-took-my-daughter-father-of-kidnapped-9-year-old-pleads-for-her-return-4601218%22%2C%22summary%22%