ations%20by%20the%20Congress%20leader.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20comparing%20a%20prime%20minister%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejaibkatra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pickpocket)%20and%20using%20the%20word%20%3Cem%3Epanauti%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20unbecoming%20of%20a%20very%20senior%20leader%20of%20a%20national%20political%20party.%20Further%2C%20the%20allegation%20of%20grant%20of%20waivers%20of%20Rs%2014%2C00%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%20past%20nine%20years%2C%20is%20asserted%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20not%20borne%20out%20on%20facts%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20poll%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fec-issues-show-cause-notice-to-rahul-over-panauti-pickpocket-jibes-at-pm-modi-101700737213882.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20has%20been%20ordered%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20EC%20on%20Saturday%2C%20November%2025%2C%20to%20file%20his%20response.%20The%20EC%E2%80%99s%20notice%20to%20Gandhi%20is%20in%20response%20to%20a%20complaint%20lodged%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20accusing%20Gandhi%20of%20resorting%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccharacter%20assassination%E2%80%9D%20of%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Barmer%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pickpocket%20never%20comes%20alone%2C%20there%20are%20three%20people.%20One%20comes%20from%20the%20front%2C%20one%20from%20the%20back%20and%20one%20from%20the%20distance%E2%80%A6%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20job%20is%20to%20divert%20your%20attention.%20He%20comes%20on%20TV%20from%20the%20front%20and%20distracts%20the%20public%20by%20raising%20topics%20of%20Hindu-Muslim%2C%20demonetisation%2C%20and%20GST.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Adani%20comes%20from%20behind%20and%20takes%20the%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20took%20exception%20to%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20against%20PM%20Modi.%20%E2%80%9CCalling%20any%20person%20for%20that%20instance%20a%20Jaibkatra%20not%20only%20amounts%20to%20vicious%20abuse%20and%20personal%20attack%20but%20also%20a%20character%20assassination%20of%20that%20person%20against%20whom%20such%20remark%20has%20been%20made%20with%20a%20clear%20intent%20to%20harm%20his%20reputation%20and%20mislead%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJP%20had%20said%20in%20its%20complaint%20filed%20before%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700740230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F26210652%2FFufcgtmX0AQCmkG.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-serves-notice-to-rahul-gandhi-over-panauti-remark-against-pm-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20called%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20'panauti%20(harbinger%20of%20bad%20luck)'%2C%20linking%20India's%20loss%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20final%20to%20the%20latter's%20presence%20at%20the%20Ahmedabad%20stadium.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fec-serves-notice-to-rahul-gandhi-over-panauti-remark-against-pm-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22XpressBees%20joins%20ONDC%20networks%2C%20expands%20services%20to%2020%2C000%20pin%20codes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700740226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F07%2Ffull%2F1699365989-8382.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fxpressbees-joins-ondc-networks-expands-services-to-20-000-pin-codes-123112300731_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22XpressBees'%20technology-driven%20approach%20allows%20seamless%20integration%20with%20online%20marketplaces%20and%20retailers.%20This%20enhances%20the%20end-to-end%20customer%20experience%22%2C%