e-dutch-pm-13014172%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%20often%20called%20the%20Netherlands'%20answer%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20appears%20to%20have%20won%20the%20Dutch%20election%20-%20but%20who%20is%20the%20inflammatory%20political%20outsider%20and%20what%20does%20he%20want%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A467%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fgeert-wilders-who-is-controversial-anti-islam-election-winner-and-will-he-become-dutch-pm-13014172%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel-Palestine%3A%20Peace%20is%20Always%20Possible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03120804%2Fisrael-palestine.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20when%20such%20things%20were%20still%20possible%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20accompanied%20a%20group%20of%20Indians%20and%20Pakistanis%20to%20Brussels%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Berlin%20to%20look%20at%20EU%20institutions%20of%20shared%20sovereignty%20and%20listen%20to%20German%20experiences.%20At%20a%20lunch%20in%20Berlin%2C%20a%20senior%20German%20official%20said%20something%20both%20smart%20and%20wise%20about%20peacemaking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20decades%2C%20he%20said%2C%20even%20before%20the%20Franco-German%20war%20of%201870-71%2C%20every%20generation%20of%20Germans%20and%20the%20French%20knew%20they%20would%20be%20going%20to%20war%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20they%20inevitably%20did.%20It%20was%20only%20through%20a%20peace%20agreement%20after%20World%20War%20II%20that%20this%20ended.%20Given%20this%20history%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20tell%20Indians%20and%20Pakistanis%2C%20except%20that%20he%20hoped%20we%20would%20be%20smarter%20than%20the%20Europeans%20and%20find%20a%20pathway%20to%20peace%20faster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20years%20later%2C%20again%20in%20Berlin%2C%20an%20Israeli%20journalist%20told%20me%20about%20how%20she%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%20tasked%20with%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20framework%20for%20dealing%20with%20the%20complicated%20issue%20of%20Jerusalem.%20This%20was%20part%20of%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20informal%20group%20brought%20together%20by%20civil%20society.%20She%20had%2C%20she%20said%2C%20been%20very%20sceptical%20that%20something%20so%20deeply%20polarising%20even%20in%20such%20an%20unofficial%20group%20could%20be%20discussed%20fruitfully.%20But%20over%20three%20days%20of%20intense%20discussion%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20what%20they%20thought%20was%20a%20workable%20proposal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20mention%20this%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20recent%20proposal%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20hostage%20exchange%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas.%20Most%20commentators%2C%20rightly%2C%20emphasise%20that%20this%20is%20far%20from%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20also%20highlighted%20%E2%80%93%20and%20even%20further%20from%20any%20prospect%20of%20peace.%20While%20this%20is%20true%2C%20we%20must%20always%20bear%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20reason%20that%20peace%20is%20elusive%20is%20not%20because%20it%20is%20impossible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeace%20is%20always%20possible%2C%20and%20even%20the%20most%20contentious%20issues%20can%20be%20worked%20out.%20The%20only%20real%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20principal%20political%20actors%20are%20sincerely%20willing%20to%20work%20towards%20peace%2C%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20hard%20decisions%20required%20to%20mean%20that%20it%20is%20a%20real%2C%20honourable%2C%20and%20durable%20peace.%20But%20once%20that%20is%20in%20place%2C%20even%20the%20most%20difficult%20issues%20seem%20to%20disappear%20so%20completely%20it%20is%20as%20if%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20for%20hostility%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20region%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fplace%2FAlsace-Lorraine%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAlsace-Lorraine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20was%20the%20principal%20bone%20of%20contention%20of%20the%20Franco-German%20War%20of%201870-71%2C%20and%20continued%20to%20be%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20war%20until%20World%20War%20II%20has%20been%20totally%20peaceful%20since%201945.%20A%20small%20region%20over%20whose%20control%20Germany%20and%20France%20expended%20countless%20lives%20and%20brought%20the%20world%20to%20war%20now%20has%20borders%20so%20porous%20between%20both%20countries%20that%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20cross%20them%20without%20realising%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20will%20point%20to%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20the%20rise%2C%20fall%20and%20horrors%20of%20the%20Nazi%20regime%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20terrible%20destruction%20that%20World%20War%20I%20and%20World%20War%20II%20inflicted%20on%20Europe%20as%20the%20motivating%20reason%20for%20the%20long%20peace.%20Again%2C%20this%20is%20true%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20that%20the%20Germans%20and%20the%20French%20could%20not%20have%20figured%20out%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20to%20the%20dispute%20before%20all%20of%20this.%20That%20they%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20millions%20over%20seven%20decades%20of%20warfare%20to%20learn%20that%20they%20could%20share%20the%20land%20without%20feeling%20threatened%20is%20an%20indictment%20of%20European%20thinking%20and%20war-mongering.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20justification%20for%20the%20lives%20lost%20and%20ruined%20over%20such%20a%20long%20period.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Israel-Palestine%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20any%20number%20of%20conflicts%20around%20the%20world%2C%20we%20are%20told%20the%20horrors%20that%20people%20have%20lived%20through%20and%20the%20unspeakable%20crimes%20committed%20by%20various%20sides%2C%20make%20peace%20impossible.%20This%20is%20only%20an%20excuse%20for%20more%20war%2C%20for%20more%20misery.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20is%20clear%20about%20the%20terrible%20costs%20of%20war%20on%20ordinary%20people%20is%20the%20absolute%20necessity%20that%20such%20horrors%20do%20not%20happen%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWar%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20often%20a%20choice%20that%20leads%20to%20more%20war.%20Let%20us%20not%20seek%20to%20excuse%20the%20political%20leaders%20for%20the%20bad%20choices%20they%20make%20by%20suggesting%20that%20peace%20is%20impossible.%20It%20is%20never%20true.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700733374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03120804%2Fisrael-palestine.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-peace-is-always-possible%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22War%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20often%20a%20choice%20that%20leads%20to%20more%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-peace-is-always-possible%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Al%20Shifa%20hospital%20director%20arrested%2C%20Hamas%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700733360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-dr-muhammed-abu-salmiya_6369382.jpg%3F20231123115157%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdirector-of-al-shifa-hospital-in-gaza-city-arrested-hamas-says-13014157%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20director%20of%20Gaza's%20largest%20hospital%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A171%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fdirector-of-al-shifa-hospital-in-gaza-city-arrested-hamas-says-13014157%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdirector-of-al-shifa-hospital-in-gaza-city-arrested-hamas-says-13014157%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdirector-of-al-shifa-hospital-in-gaza-city-arrested-hamas-says-13014157%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kashmiri%20Journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%20Returns%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23182451%2FFahad-Shah.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Kashmiri%20journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fafter-nearly-2-years-jk-hc-grants-bail-to-kashmir-walla-editor-fahad-shah%5C%22%3Ewas%20granted%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20terrorism%20case%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20last%20week%2C%20returned%20home%20on%20Thursday%20(November%2023)%20after%20spending%20nearly%20two%20years%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20family%20sources%2C%20his%20brother%2C%20Peerzada%20Akib%20Shah%2C%20had%20gone%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20Jammu%2C%20where%20Fahad%20Shah%20was%20languishing%20in%20Kot%20Balwal%20jail%20after%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20(SIA)%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20article%20in%20his%20digital%20news%20outlet%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkib%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20contractor%2C%20furnished%20the%20bail%20bond%20and%20a%20surety%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each%20and%20completed%20other%20legal%20formalities%2C%20after%20which%20the%20jail%20authorities%20released%20his%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20good%20to%20be%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20his%20first%20interview%20after%20walking%20out%20of%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20different%20to%20be%20with%20your%20family%20and%20friends.%20I%20have%20been%20through%20a%20lot%20in%20these%20long%20years%20which%20has%20changed%20me%20at%20multiple%20levels.%20My%20health%20has%20also%20deteriorated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20started%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20blog%20in%202009%2C%20lives%20in%20the%20Aanchar%20locality%20in%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Soura%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20home%20was%20swarmed%20by%20relatives%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20seen%20carrying%20sweets%20%E2%80%93%20and%20friends%20soon%20after%20the%20news%20of%20his%20return%20broke%20on%20Thursday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20the%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20said%20that%20it%20welcomes%20the%20release%20of%20Shah%20while%20urging%20the%20authorities%20to%20lift%20the%20ban%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20website%2C%20which%20was%20put%20in%20effect%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EKashmiri%20journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%20has%20returned%20home%20Thursday%20after%20nearly%20two%20years%20in%20detention%20on%20terror%20charges%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPJ%20welcomes%20his%20release%20on%20bail.%20All%20charges%20against%20Shah%20must%20be%20dropped%20and%20the%20ban%20on%20his%20publication%20The%20Kashmir%20Walla%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftkwmag%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40tkwmag%3C%2Fa%3E%20revoked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeCjFpf1SRd%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeCjFpf1SRd%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FX7NtyiTNnY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FX7NtyiTNnY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20CPJ%20Asia%20(%40CPJAsia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCPJAsia%2Fstatus%2F1727612087667462296%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20has%20extensively%20written%20on%20Kashmir%20for%20national%20and%20international%20media%20outlets%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20SIA%2C%20the%20elite%20counterterrorism%20agency%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%2C%20on%20charges%20of%20terror%20funding%20and%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20country%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIA%20had%20filed%20the%20case%20at%20the%20CIJ%20Police%20Station%20in%20Jammu%20in%202020%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20article%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20shackles%20of%20slavery%20will%20break%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20appeared%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202011%20and%20which%20the%20agency%20sought%20to%20describe%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cact%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20of%20the%20controversial%20article%2C%20Aala%20Fazili%2C%20a%20scholar%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pharmaceutical%20Department%2C%20was%20also%20booked%20and%20arrested%20by%20the%20SIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20special%20court%20framed%20charges%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20outlet%20was%20banned%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffahad-shah-jammu-kashmir-high-court-order%5C%22%3Ethe%20high%20court%20struck%20down%20the%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20country%20and%20terror%20funding%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20against%20Shah%20while%20linking%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20controversial%20article%20to%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20his%20bail%20application%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20observed%20that%20invoking%20charges%20of%20terrorism%20against%20Shah%20for%20an%2011-year-old%20article%20%E2%80%9Ccollide%5Bs%5D%20head%20long%20with%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20enshrined%20in%20Article%2019%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20prosecution%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20article%20was%20a%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20India%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20observed%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20argument%20is%20accepted%2C%20it%20would%20literally%20turn%20criminal%20law%20on%20its%20head.%20It%20would%20mean%20that%20any%20criticism%20of%20the%20central%20government%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20terrorist%20act%20because%20the%20honour%20of%20India%20is%20its%20incorporeal%20property.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20has%20also%20been%20booked%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20in%20three%20cases%20related%20to%20the%20reporting%20of%20two%20encounters%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%2C%20as%20well%20as%20of%20allegations%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20forcing%20the%20management%20of%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Shopian%20to%20organise%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20courts%20in%20all%20three%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20also%20quashed%20the%20proceedings%20against%20Shah%20under%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA)%20while%20castigating%20the%20authorities%20for%20depriving%20him%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%20and%20legal%20rights%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20termed%20the%20grounds%20of%20his%20PSA%20detention%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmere%20surmise%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cvague%20and%20bald%20assertions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20International%20has%20termed%20the%20PSA%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20to%20curb%20the%20menace%20of%20timber%20smuggling%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20insurgency%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Clawless%20law%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20used%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Crevolving%20door%E2%80%9D%20policy%20for%20suspects%20against%20whom%20security%20agencies%20have%20little%20to%20no%20evidence%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20them%20%E2%80%9Cout%20of%20circulation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700732392000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23182451%2FFahad-Shah.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmiri-journalist-fahad-shah-returns-home%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shah%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20on%20terrorism%20charges%20for%20publishing%20an%20article%20in%20his%20news%20outlet%20The%20Kashmir%20Walla%20in%202011.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmiri-journalist-fahad-shah-returns-home%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%20Contest%20Between%20'Dharma'%20and%20'Raj%20Dharma'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23141227%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERajasthan%2C%20where%20the%20election%20is%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20for%20the%20state%20assembly%20on%20November%2025%20is%20witnessing%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20employ%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Hindutva%20as%20its%20core%20plans%20to%20garner%20votes.%20There%20is%20no%20primacy%20given%20to%20regional%20leaders%20in%20such%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20pattern%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20party%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20issues%20hardly%20form%20part%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign.%20While%20media%20reports%20suggest%20that%20there%20is%20momentum%20for%20possible%20change%20of%20regime%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20by%20unseating%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20there%20is%20discernible%20trend%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20the%20continuance%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20432px)%2085vw%2C%20432px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22356%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGehlot%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20schemes%20versus%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20promises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20there%20is%20a%20neck-to-neck%20contest%20between%20Congress%20and%20BJP.%20The%20existing%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20seven%20guarantees%20in%20its%20election%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20which%2C%20among%20others%20things%2C%20include%C2%A0%20Rs%2010%2C000%20every%20year%20to%20the%20female%20head%20of%20the%20family%20under%20the%20Griha%20Lakshmi%20Yojana%20guarantee%2C%20cow%20dung%20at%20Rs%202%20kg%20under%20the%20Gowdhan%20project%2C%20free%20laptops%20and%20tablets%20to%20first-year%20government%20college%20students%20%E2%80%93%20have%20gained%20traction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gehlot%20government%E2%80%99s%20scheme%20to%20give%20Rs%2025%20lakhs%20to%20people%20for%20medical%20treatment%20and%20its%20assurances%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20(OPS)%20and%20providing%20free%20education%20has%20become%20very%20popular.%20In%20its%20manifesto%20released%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20four%20days%20before%20the%20elections%2C%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20enhance%20the%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20promise%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20and%2C%20among%20other%20promises%2C%20assured%20that%20it%20will%20implement%20MSP%20for%20crops%20based%20on%20the%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20formula.%20It%20promises%20to%20give%20four%20lakh%20government%20jobs%2C%20and%2010%20lakh%20other%20jobs%2C%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20and%20give%20cooking%20gas%20cylinders%20to%20some%20families%20at%20Rs%20450%20per%20cylinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20promises%20to%20enact%20a%20legislation%20guaranteeing%20the%20right%20to%20shelter.%20In%20contrast%2C%20BJP%20in%20manifesto%20has%20assured%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500.%20Vey%20strikingly%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mention%20restoration%20of%20OPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticism%20of%20Gehlot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20regime%20was%20widely%20criticised%20by%20youth%20and%20people%20of%20the%20state%20on%20the%20paper%20leak%20issue%20which%20led%20to%20the%20cancellation%20of%20competitive%20exams%20for%20filling%20vacancies%20at%20government%20jobs.%20There%20is%20also%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Congress%20MLAs%20even%20though%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20personally%20enjoys%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20is%20defensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20media%20commentators%20wonder%20how%20it%20is%20that%20in%20none%20of%20the%20BJP-ruled%20states%20gas%20cylinders%20are%20available%20for%20as%20cheap%20as%20Rs%20500.%20How%20can%20the%20party%20make%20such%20a%20promise%2C%20it%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Modi%20Guarantees%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20fashioned%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20guarantees%20in%20Karnataka%20where%20it%20won%20a%20decisive%20mandate%20and%20BJP%20lost%20power.%20It%20is%20quite%20striking%20that%20while%20Congress%20calls%20those%20guarantees%20as%20those%20of%20the%20party%2C%20to%20the%20people%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%20names%20the%20promises%20it%20has%20stated%20as%20%E2%80%98Modi%E2%80%99s%20Guarantees%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJP%20follows%20the%20Congress%20example%20of%20%C2%A0giving%20guarantees%20it%20centres%20these%20around%20Modi.%20The%20unmistakable%20centrality%20of%20Modi%20in%20the%20template%20of%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20projected%20before%20the%20electorate%20to%20appear%20as%20if%20Modi%20is%20the%20driving%20force%20for%20every%20thing%20associated%20with%20party%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20strategy%20is%20best%20manifested%20in%20an%20election%20rally%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20in%20Rajasthan%20which%20began%20from%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20where%20there%20were%20bomb%20blasts%20some%20years%20ago%20and%20traversed%20through%20the%20area.%20Many%20wondered%20if%20the%20route%20would%20give%20birth%20to%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20beheading%20of%20a%20Hindu%20tailor%20Kanhiya%20Lal%20in%20Rajasthan%20last%20year%20by%20Muslims%20because%20of%20the%20alleged%20insult%20of%20Prophet%20Mohammad%20by%20a%20BJP%20spokesperson%20has%20been%20frequently%20invoked%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20appeal%20to%20voters.%20One%20BJP%20leader%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20victory%20of%20Congress%20will%20cause%20celebrations%20in%20Pakistan.%20Such%20statements%20might%20cause%20polarisation%20of%20voters%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20in%20the%20state%20do%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20assured%20of%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%2C%20apart%20from%20solely%20relying%20on%20local%20leaders%20and%20taking%20up%20local%20socio-economic%20issues%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20voters%20through%20its%20guarantees%20and%20manifesto%2C%20which%20it%20claimed%20is%20based%20on%20the%20rights%20of%20people%2C%20regardless%20of%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%20personality%20Vijaya%20Vidrohi%20succinctly%20put%20the%20electoral%20contest%20of%20%E2%80%98Congress%20vs%20BJP%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20contest%20between%20%E2%80%98Raj%20Dharma%20vs%20Dharma%E2%80%99.%20While%20Raj%20Dharma%20represents%20the%20rule%20or%20governance%20for%20promoting%20welfare%20of%20people%20without%20any%20discrimination%20based%20on%20their%20identities%2C%20the%20Dharma%20here%20represents%20Hindutva%20strategy%20which%20does%20not%20include%20Muslims.%20He%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20eventually%20people%20might%20get%20persuaded%20more%20by%20Raj%20Dharma%20rather%20than%20mere%20Dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20quoted%20a%20famous%20line%20from%20the%20folklore%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERub%20Ruthe%2C%20Raj%20Na%20Ruthe%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGod%20might%20be%20angry%2C%20but%20the%20King%20should%20not%20be%20angry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20regional%20leaders%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20under%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20has%20relegated%20regional%20leaders%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20states%20to%20secondary%20status%20and%20in%20Rajasthan%20it%20has%20been%20done%20to%20three-time%20chief%20minister%20and%20highly%20influential%20leader%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia.%20She%20was%20reportedly%20not%20given%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20party%20manifesto%20at%20the%20time%20of%20its%20release%20when%20she%20was%20there%20on%20the%20dais%20with%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda.%20Eventually%20someone%20gave%20a%20copy%20to%20her%20and%20she%20stood%20with%20it%20in%20hand%2C%20without%20displaying%20it%20for%20media%20coverage.%20The%20visual%20message%20is%20clear.%20She%20is%20also%20not%20visiting%20constituencies%20other%20than%20her%20own%20for%20campaigns%20and%20on%20one%20occasion%20publicly%20declared%20that%20she%20would%20retire%20as%20her%20son%20is%20now%20able%20to%20take%20care%20of%20himself%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20marginalisation%20of%20a%20key%20regional%20leader%20like%20her%20in%20the%20electoral%20battle%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20reliance%20of%20the%20party%20on%20Hindutva%20and%20Modi%20and%20not%20on%20its%20own%20manifesto%20leads%20one%20to%20wonder%20which%20brand%20of%20campaigns%20will%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20Served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700729008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F23141227%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-rajasthan-a-contest-between-dharma-and-raj-dharma%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20marginalised%20key%20leaders.%20The%20Congress%20has%20focused%20on%20an%20ambitious%20manifesto.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-rajasthan-a-contest-between-dharma-and-raj-dharma%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shane%20MacGowan%20'out%20of%20hospital'%20after%20months%20in%20intensive%20care%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700727840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-shane-macgowan-hospital_6369200.jpg%3F20231123090846%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fshane-macgowans-wife-says-the-pogues-frontman-is-out-of-hospital-13014073%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shane%20MacGowan's%20wife%20has%20said%20Th