at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20looking%20for%20some%20healthy%20food%20to%20serve%20as%20snacks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20market%20in%20search%20of%20some%20unadulterated%20food.%20All%20I%20saw%20was%20frozen%20and%20packaged%20food%2C%20which%20was%20highly%20processed%20with%20many%20preservatives%20and%20harmful%20additives%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rukhsaar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFailing%20to%20find%20anything%20appealing%2C%20she%20thought%20of%20working%20on%20something%20without%20preservatives%2C%20for%20busy%20mothers.%20After%20completing%20her%20PhD%2C%20she%20started%20researching%20how%20to%20make%20healthy%20frozen%20snacks%20without%20additives%20and%20started%20experimenting%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20frozen%20chicken%20nuggets%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20They%20are%20all%20loaded%20with%20additives%20and%20meat%20fillers.%20I%20worked%20on%20how%20to%20preserve%20food%20in%20a%20natural%20way%20and%20studied%20how%20to%20increase%20the%20shelf%20life.%20My%20degree%20helped%20in%20recipe%20formulation%20and%20standardisation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20took%20her%20almost%20eight%20months%20to%20study%20and%20work%20on%20the%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20experimented%20with%20chicken%20strips%2C%20nuggets%2C%20popcorn%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekalari%20%3C%2Fem%3Echeese%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20became%20a%20big%20hit.%20She%20also%20served%20her%20snacks%20at%20an%20exhibition%20at%20the%20Sheri%20Kashmir%20International%20Convention%20Centre%20(SKICC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20response%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20convert%20her%20experiments%20at%20home%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20venture.%20On%203%20August%2C%202019%2C%20she%20launched%20%E2%80%98Khalis%20Foods%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%2C%20frozen%20food%20venture%20from%20Pampore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20life%20had%20oth